rsemtpm_nikos_chr1 <- rsemtpm_nikos[rsemtpm_nikos$seqnames == 'chr1']

first_genome_coord <- min(rsemtpm_nikos_chr1$start)
final_genome_coord <- max(rsemtpm_nikos_chr1$end)

bin_size <- 20000000

genome_bins <- as.integer(ceiling((final_genome_coord - first_genome_coord) / bin_size))

bins <- c(0)
counter <- 0
for (i in 1:genome_bins) {
  counter <- counter + bin_size
  bins <- append(bins, counter)
}

rsemtpm_nikos_chr1_binsummed <- colnames(rsemtpm_nikos_chr1[,-c(1:6)])
